        "q1": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>Most people feel the initial lift within 15–30 minutes. The caffeine and L-Theanine activate quickly. Longer-term benefits from Lion's Mane and Cordyceps build over 1–2 weeks of consistent use.</p>",
