          },
          "type": "question"
        },
        "q3": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>DayShift already contains 120mg of caffeine. You can combine it with coffee but be mindful of your total caffeine intake. We'd suggest skipping the extra coffee for the first week to assess your personal response.</p>",
